definition: having superior power and influence, be larger in number, quantity, power, status or importance
details:
adjective
- having superior power and influence
= synonyms: overriding
verb
- be larger in number, quantity, power, status or importance
= synonyms: rule, reign, prevail, dominate
- appear very large or occupy a commanding position
= example: appear very large or occupy a commanding position
= synonyms: hulk, loom, tower
